[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":199},["ShallowReactive",2],{"settings":3,"la-maitrise-des-3-armes":69},{"id":4,"uid":5,"url":5,"type":6,"href":7,"tags":8,"first_publication_date":9,"last_publication_date":10,"slugs":11,"linked_documents":13,"lang":14,"alternate_languages":15,"data":16},"af9qgBAAACcASJmy",null,"settings","https:\u002F\u002Faikido-traditionnel-cotiere.cdn.prismic.io\u002Fapi\u002Fv2\u002Fdocuments\u002Fsearch?ref=akS0mhIAACoAR8GB&q=%5B%5B%3Ad+%3D+at%28document.id%2C+%22af9qgBAAACcASJmy%22%29+%5D%5D",[],"2026-05-09T17:11:04+0000","2026-07-01T06:32:58+0000",[12],"menu-principal",[],"fr-fr",[],{"site_title":17,"site_description":18,"site_image":19,"navigation":29},"Aïkido Traditionnel de la Cotière","Le site du Dojo d'aïkido de dagneux",{"dimensions":20,"alt":5,"copyright":5,"url":23,"id":24,"edit":25},{"width":21,"height":22},131,184,"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.prismic.io\u002Faikido-traditionnel-cotiere\u002Faf9VUaYofJOwHCJZ_main-logo.jpg?auto=format,compress","af9VUaYofJOwHCJZ",{"x":26,"y":26,"zoom":27,"background":28},0,1,"transparent",[30,43,54,63],{"id":31,"type":32,"tags":33,"lang":14,"slug":34,"first_publication_date":35,"last_publication_date":36,"url":37,"link_type":38,"key":39,"isBroken":40,"text":41,"variant":42},"af9xqhAAACgASKPZ","index",[],"accueil","2026-05-09T17:41:10+0000","2026-06-25T21:16:02+0000","\u002F","Document","8ccaa39a-debf-4883-93f1-156ce0bc7681",false,"Le Dojo","Lien",{"id":44,"type":45,"tags":46,"lang":14,"slug":47,"first_publication_date":48,"last_publication_date":49,"uid":50,"url":51,"link_type":38,"key":52,"isBroken":40,"text":53,"variant":42},"agL_7RAAACgATcrb","focuses",[],"laikido","2026-05-12T10:29:03+0000","2026-05-13T14:20:54+0000","aikido","\u002Ffocus\u002Faikido","2c918af7-a31f-4d87-a906-63d0c3dd8d72","L'Aïkido",{"id":55,"type":56,"tags":57,"lang":14,"slug":58,"first_publication_date":59,"last_publication_date":60,"link_type":38,"key":61,"isBroken":40,"text":62,"variant":42},"agMF8RAAANw7TdUG","standard",[],"cours-dessai-sans-engagement","2026-05-12T10:51:05+0000","2026-07-01T06:27:49+0000","eb53ebaf-7be1-48a6-aca2-8a14b526b244","Essai gratuit",{"link_type":64,"key":65,"url":66,"text":67,"variant":68},"Web","b4d404eb-b90c-4329-8c85-e6e98b411fb2","\u002Finscriptions","Inscriptions","Bouton",{"id":70,"uid":71,"url":72,"type":45,"href":73,"tags":74,"first_publication_date":75,"last_publication_date":76,"slugs":77,"linked_documents":79,"lang":14,"alternate_languages":80,"data":81},"agLgwRAAACcATZZo","la-maitrise-des-3-armes","\u002Ffocus\u002Fla-maitrise-des-3-armes","https:\u002F\u002Faikido-traditionnel-cotiere.cdn.prismic.io\u002Fapi\u002Fv2\u002Fdocuments\u002Fsearch?ref=akS0mhIAACoAR8GB&q=%5B%5B%3Ad+%3D+at%28document.id%2C+%22agLgwRAAACcATZZo%22%29+%5D%5D",[],"2026-05-12T08:41:52+0000","2026-06-23T13:42:54+0000",[78],"la-pratique-des-3-armes",[],[],{"title":82,"description":88,"cover":93,"slices":100,"meta_title":5,"meta_description":5,"meta_image":198},[83],{"type":84,"text":85,"spans":86,"direction":87},"heading1","La pratique des 3 armes",[],"ltr",[89],{"type":90,"text":91,"spans":92,"direction":87},"paragraph","Contrairement à une pratique purement sportive, nous enseignons l'Aïkido dans sa globalité. Vous apprendrez le maniement du Bokken (sabre en bois), du Jo (bâton) et du Tanto (couteau), piliers indispensables pour comprendre les déplacements et la précision des techniques à mains nues.",[],{"dimensions":94,"alt":5,"copyright":5,"url":97,"id":98,"edit":99},{"width":95,"height":96},2816,1536,"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.prismic.io\u002Faikido-traditionnel-cotiere\u002FagLnvKYofJOwHHC5_Gemini_Generated_Image_qp7a9eqp7a9eqp7a.png?auto=format,compress","agLnvKYofJOwHHC5",{"x":26,"y":26,"zoom":27,"background":28},[101],{"variation":102,"version":103,"items":104,"primary":105,"id":196,"slice_type":197,"slice_label":5},"default","initial",[],{"anchor":5,"title":106,"sub_title":110,"content":124,"image":128,"liens":129,"details":130,"iframe":5},[107],{"type":84,"text":108,"spans":109,"direction":87},"L'Art des Armes de l'Aïkido",[],[111],{"type":112,"text":113,"spans":114,"direction":87},"heading2","Bokken, Jo et Tanto : L'Héritage du Guerrier au Service du Mouvement",[115,118,121],{"start":26,"end":116,"type":117},6,"em",{"start":119,"end":120,"type":117},8,10,{"start":122,"end":123,"type":117},14,19,[125],{"type":90,"text":126,"spans":127,"direction":87},"En Aïkido, les armes ne sont pas de simples instruments ; elles sont le prolongement du corps et l'âme de la technique. La pratique aux armes (Bukiwaza) purifie le mouvement, aiguise l'esprit et donne tout son sens au travail à mains nues. Découvrez les trois armes traditionnelles qui sont le cœur de notre enseignement à Dagneux.",[],{},[],[131,155,176],{"content_title":132,"content_punchline":140,"content_body":145,"content_image":149,"content_link":154},[133],{"type":134,"text":135,"spans":136,"direction":87},"heading3","Le Bokken (le Sabre de Bois)",[137],{"start":138,"end":139,"type":117},3,9,[141],{"type":142,"text":143,"spans":144,"direction":87},"heading4","Là où le sabre s'arrête, l'Aïkido commence.",[],[146],{"type":90,"text":147,"spans":148,"direction":87},"Le Bokken est la réplique en bois du Katana, le sabre du samouraï. Il est l'âme des armes de l'Aïkido. Dans notre dojo, nous apprenons que chaque coupe, chaque garde (kamae), forge une structure corporelle solide et une concentration inébranlable. Sa pratique est indispensable pour comprendre les principes de distance (ma-ai), de timing (de-ai) et de coupe (cutting edge) que l'on retrouve dans toutes les projections et immobilisations à mains nues. C'est l'outil de la rigueur et de la décision.",[],{"dimensions":150,"alt":5,"copyright":5,"url":151,"id":152,"edit":153},{"width":95,"height":96},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.prismic.io\u002Faikido-traditionnel-cotiere\u002FagOGHKYofJOwHJQ-_Gemini_Generated_Image_llcp9ollcp9ollcp.png?auto=format,compress","agOGHKYofJOwHJQ-",{"x":26,"y":26,"zoom":27,"background":28},[],{"content_title":156,"content_punchline":162,"content_body":166,"content_image":170,"content_link":175},[157],{"type":134,"text":158,"spans":159,"direction":87},"Le Jo (le Bâton Moyen)",[160],{"start":138,"end":161,"type":117},5,[163],{"type":142,"text":164,"spans":165,"direction":87},"Le bâton qui ne cherche pas à briser, mais à unifier.",[],[167],{"type":90,"text":168,"spans":169,"direction":87},"Le Jo est un bâton d'environ 1,28 mètre. Sa simplicité cache une polyvalence redoutable. Il n'a ni tranchant ni pointe définie, ce qui le rend fluide et interchangeable. En Aïkido, la pratique du Jo (Jodo) enseigne l'adaptabilité, la fluidité des hanches et la précision des attaques (frappes et piques). Contrairement au sabre, le Jo peut se saisir par ses deux extrémités, offrant une multitude d'enchaînements (suburi) et de contre-attaques. Il est l'arme de l'harmonie et du mouvement perpétuel.",[],{"dimensions":171,"alt":5,"copyright":5,"url":172,"id":173,"edit":174},{"width":95,"height":96},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.prismic.io\u002Faikido-traditionnel-cotiere\u002FagOHMaYofJOwHJSF_Gemini_Generated_Image_ur7znaur7znaur7z.png?auto=format,compress","agOHMaYofJOwHJSF",{"x":26,"y":26,"zoom":27,"background":28},[],{"content_title":177,"content_punchline":182,"content_body":186,"content_image":190,"content_link":195},[178],{"type":134,"text":179,"spans":180,"direction":87},"Le Tanto (le Couteau de Bois)",[181],{"start":138,"end":119,"type":117},[183],{"type":142,"text":184,"spans":185,"direction":87},"Face à la menace la plus proche, l'équilibre intérieur est la seule arme.",[],[187],{"type":90,"text":188,"spans":189,"direction":87},"Le Tanto est un poignard ou couteau. Dans la pratique traditionnelle, l'attaque au couteau représente la menace la plus rapprochée et la plus dangereuse. La pratique face au Tanto (Tanto-dori) est un test de sang-froid et d'efficacité technique. Elle force le pratiquant à parfaire sa désaxation (tai sabaki), son enracinement et son déséquilibre immédiat de l'attaquant. Elle nous enseigne que même face à un danger extrême, la réponse de l'Aïkido n'est pas la violence, mais la gestion calme du centre et la neutralisation sans haine.",[],{"dimensions":191,"alt":5,"copyright":5,"url":192,"id":193,"edit":194},{"width":95,"height":96},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.prismic.io\u002Faikido-traditionnel-cotiere\u002FagOH8KYofJOwHJSU_Gemini_Generated_Image_12yjw12yjw12yjw1.png?auto=format,compress","agOH8KYofJOwHJSU",{"x":26,"y":26,"zoom":27,"background":28},[],"focus_content$abb233e5-f92b-405e-9552-79844910304a","focus_content",{},1782889219104]